It's not much to see if you're just looking to sightsee. You need to participate if you visit &quot;Calle de dulces!&quot; 

They got all sorts of candies. Lots of chocolate! Chocolate covered nuts, raisins, mango, pineapple, Carmel apples, plantain chips, and so much more. 

It's hard to walk by all these stores without buying a lot!
